# Mobile (Expo) rules

- Backend URL via `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` (default `http://localhost:8080`)
- Physical device: use LAN IP (e.g. `http://192.168.x.x:8080`), not `localhost`
- Entry point: `mobile/index.ts` → `mobile/App.tsx`
- Run: `cd mobile && npx expo start` — press `w` for web, scan QR for device
- No new Expo modules without explicit approval; check if bare React Native is needed
- TypeScript: avoid `any`
- Do not run `expo eject` or switch to bare workflow during the hackathon
